propel.core.collections.buffers

Interface IBuffer<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CircularBuffer, LRUBuffer, SharedBuffer

    public interface IBuffer<T>
extends ReifiedIterable<T>
    The interface that buffers follow. Buffers are LIFO-type containers, very much like queues, but distinctively they have a set size.
